Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A FATHER AND SON CLASH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give in!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Dai, the Hero!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You still resist your father?! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He struck me while I was shielded\Nby my Dragonic Aura?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's crest is on his fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Impossible! This can't be!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In thousands of years\Nof Dragon Knight history{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the light of the crest to appear\Nanywhere other than the forehead...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's never happened before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human spirit?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this Soara's will?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?!\NWhy is the Dragon Crest on his fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Dai did it by his own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To escape Baran's mind control...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and to gain greater power than him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he realized he had to move\Nthe power of his crest from his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,His full Aura power may be weaker,\Nbut when it's focused in a single point,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,each attack is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is such a miracle possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt a normal Dragon Knight can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Baran seems taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taken so much from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My dearest things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you are my dad,\NI'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your tongue, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speculating, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the blood of Dai's human half\Nbrought on this miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His feelings for his friend\Nignited a fire in his human heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,driving the Dragon\Nand Darkling powers into his fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And this gave Dai control of his power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean right now, Dai is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have full control\Nover the power of the Dragon Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soara...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even you... Are you saying I was wrong?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You're right!\NEvery one of Dai's attacks is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!\NAs if a child could beat his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to back down\Nor I'll open a hole in your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fire my Crest Beam at full power,\Nit can carve a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Dino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The others are fair game...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Dai! Don't anger Baran any further!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He hasn't shown his full power yet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, let me cast Hoimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget me. See to Crocodine and Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Popp to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never used it before,\Nbut I want to test a spell on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It's beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest battle in the world\Nbeyond anything we can fathom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. So this is\Nthe ferocity of Dragon Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We must make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Dragon Knight we believe is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right. Dai's doomed at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, Baran's been holding back\Nso as not to kill Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with us, he probably held back\Nbecause we used to be allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But now he's a Dragonoid,\Na Killing Demon Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If provoked enough,\Nhe'll kill anyone, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's his own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Doru Aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABREAK{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Dragon's mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! Doru Aura compresses\Nmassive amounts of Dragonic Aura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and fires it as a spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Dai, dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}Doru Aura!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What power!\NThis isn't even a spell anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You dodged with a Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped the Doru Aura energy field\Nwith a sudden short Rura spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Toberura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you can't beat Baran in the air!\NHe has wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he choosing to fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If Baran fires that Super Spell down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we and the people of Teran\Nwill be reduced to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Dai took to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in his anger,\NDai is still our Dai inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a monster like Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and heal us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is to stand!\NI can't just do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll withstand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you can't cast a spell\Nthat strong more than twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I withstand this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No being can withstand\Na Dragon Knight's Doru Aura at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never been used on a Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Dragon Knight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your nonsense, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this and begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}Doru Aura!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon within me,\Nnow's the time to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus everything I have to defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He withstood it! That Super Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing left now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When Dragon Knights fight\Nwith Dragonic Auras at full strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,normal weapons and armour\Ncan't endure the power and burn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, you've focused\Nall of your power in your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No weapon in the world\Ncan endure such immense power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My Demon Dragon Blade is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only sword in the world\Nthat can endure the Dragonic Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Only this sword can endure\Na full-powered swing of a Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not have the Magic Power to cast\NDoru Aura, but victory is in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slice you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was known as the Beast King!\NI don't intend to just lie around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see to Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if I can cast\Nsuch a major spell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I don't succeed, Popp will...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods, bless us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In thy name, let the soul of this one\Nwhose life has burned out be restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Zaoraru!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zaoraru! The resurrection spell\Nsaid to bring back the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Popp can be saved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with an experienced Cleric,\Nthe success rate is less than 50 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's up to the Princess's magic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to us, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to cut my arm\Nyou'll have to use Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Raiden spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Die quietly\Nlike the bag of bones you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the gods can interfere\Nin this battle between father and son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit around.\NIf I can move, it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, wake up! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your strength. I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:53.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:08.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:16.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai is on the defense, but thanks to\Nbackup from Hyunckel, he holds out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Leona continues\Nto desperately cast Zing on Popp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle's conclusion approaches.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will Dai be able\Nto defeat his father Baran?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lightning shall sever\Nthe ties of father and son.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Farewell to the Father"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
